snippets.title: DocumentLinkService listLinkedTargets Sample
snippets.description: Return all target document-links from the document.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService listLinkedSources Sample
snippets.description: Return all source document-links from the document.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService createDocumentLink Sample
snippets.description: Create a link between a source document and a target document.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService deleteDocumentLink Sample
snippets.description: Remove the link between the source and target documents.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService createDocumentSchema Sample
snippets.description: Creates a document schema.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService updateDocumentSchema Sample
snippets.description: Updates a Document Schema. Returns INVALID_ARGUMENT if the name of the Document Schema is non-empty and does not equal the existing name. Supports only appending new properties, adding new ENUM possible values, and updating the [EnumTypeOptions.validation_check_disabled][google.cloud.contentwarehouse.v1.EnumTypeOptions.validation_check_disabled] flag for ENUM possible values. Updating existing properties will result into INVALID_ARGUMENT.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService getDocumentSchema Sample
snippets.description: Gets a document schema. Returns NOT_FOUND if the document schema does not exist.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService deleteDocumentSchema Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a document schema. Returns NOT_FOUND if the document schema does not exist. Returns BAD_REQUEST if the document schema has documents depending on it.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService listDocumentSchemas Sample
snippets.description: Lists document schemas.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService createDocument Sample
snippets.description: Creates a document.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService getDocument Sample
snippets.description: Gets a document. Returns NOT_FOUND if the document does not exist.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService updateDocument Sample
snippets.description: Updates a document. Returns INVALID_ARGUMENT if the name of the document is non-empty and does not equal the existing name.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService deleteDocument Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a document. Returns NOT_FOUND if the document does not exist.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService searchDocuments Sample
snippets.description: Searches for documents using provided [SearchDocumentsRequest][google.cloud.contentwarehouse.v1.SearchDocumentsRequest]. This call only returns documents that the caller has permission to search against.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService fetchAcl Sample
snippets.description: Gets the access control policy for a resource. Returns NOT_FOUND error if the resource does not exist. Returns an empty policy if the resource exists but does not have a policy set.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService setAcl Sample
snippets.description: Sets the access control policy for a resource. Replaces any existing policy.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService createRuleSet Sample
snippets.description: Creates a ruleset.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService getRuleSet Sample
snippets.description: Gets a ruleset. Returns NOT_FOUND if the ruleset does not exist.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService updateRuleSet Sample
snippets.description: Updates a ruleset. Returns INVALID_ARGUMENT if the name of the ruleset is non-empty and does not equal the existing name.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService deleteRuleSet Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a ruleset. Returns NOT_FOUND if the document does not exist.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService listRuleSets Sample
snippets.description: Lists rulesets.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService createSynonymSet Sample
snippets.description: Creates a SynonymSet for a single context. Throws an ALREADY_EXISTS exception if a synonymset already exists for the context.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService getSynonymSet Sample
snippets.description: Gets a SynonymSet for a particular context. Throws a NOT_FOUND exception if the Synonymset does not exist

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService updateSynonymSet Sample
snippets.description: Remove the existing SynonymSet for the context and replaces it with a new one. Throws a NOT_FOUND exception if the SynonymSet is not found.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService deleteSynonymSet Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a SynonymSet for a given context. Throws a NOT_FOUND exception if the SynonymSet is not found.

snippets.title: DocumentLinkService listSynonymSets Sample
snippets.description: Returns all SynonymSets (for all contexts) for the specified location.
